summary: Completed final comprehensive testing of Telegram Bot UI/UX redesign (Iteration 6). All 16 backend tests passed successfully (100% success rate). Validated all required components: backend startup, API endpoints, translation strings with 4 languages, keyboard menu structures, and key function implementations.

POST /api/time-check responds correctly - Time check endpoint working with all required fields
